в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ api/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ routes.py           # Router aggregation
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ users.py            # User registration, login, profile
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ rooms.py            # Room CRUD + membership
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ messages.py         # Message history
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ files.py            # File upload/download
