в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.py                # Click CLI entry point
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config.py              # Config + token storage (~/.termtalk/)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ commands/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ auth.py            # register / login / logout
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ chat.py            # chat command + slash commands
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ friends.py         # friend management
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ users.py           # online users / status
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ config_cmd.py      # configure server URL
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ network/
